-- MOVES-UK's Threadneedle Investments appoints client portfolio manager
-- 
-- Thu Jun 26, 2014 07:14AM EDT
-- None



June 26 (Reuters) - UK-based asset manager Threadneedle Investments named Craig Nowrie as client portfolio manager in its multi-asset allocation team.

Nowrie will join the firm on June 30 in its London office and will report to Toby Nangle, head of multi-asset allocation.